markdownRemark.html:
It’s audition season! Want to join EUSO? Sign up via this link to receive your orchestral excerpt and the access to the Google Folder.

From there, you can send us your recordings of a piece and the orchestral excerpt.

Quality of your recording doesn’t matter, we’re just looking for a visual and audio! The deadline for submitting your audition is THIS FRIDAY at NOON.
